"use strict";(self.webpackChunkdocs=self.webpackChunkdocs||[]).push([[36647],{65698:(e,n,i)=>{i.r(n),i.d(n,{data:()=>d});const d={key:"v-f30d73a0",path:"/GDAL/%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB.html",title:"定义地理坐标系",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[],git:{updatedTime:1655779244e3,contributors:[{name:"panzhiyue",email:"30484534+panzhiyue@users.noreply.github.com",commits:1}]},filePathRelative:"GDAL/定义地理坐标系.md"}},91885:(e,n,i)=>{i.r(n),i.d(n,{default:()=>s});const d=(0,i(57293).uE)('<h1 id="定义地理坐标系" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#定义地理坐标系" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 定义地理坐标系</h1><p>1.一个地理坐标系包含的信息有一个大地基准(里面含有一个使用长半轴和扁率的倒数来表示的椭球体),一个中央线(通常是本初子午线,也就是0度经线 <code>Greenwich</code>),此外还有一个角度的度量单位,使用度作为单位而不是弧度,如果含有这些信息,我们就可以构造一个有效的地理坐标系统,代码如下:</p><div class="language-c# ext-c# line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-c#"><code>OGRSpatialReference oSRS;\noSRS.SetGeogCs(&quot;Mygeographic coordinate system&quot;,   //定义的地理坐标系的名称\n               &quot;WGS_1984&quot;,                         //是一个定义大地基准的关键词,注意:这里的大地基准必须是一个有效的大地基准,不能随便指定\n               &quot;My WGS84 Spheroid&quot;,                //定义的椭球体的名字\n               SRS_WGS84_SEMIMAJOR,                //（OGR定义的常数）WGS84椭球体的长半轴(6378137米)\n               SRS_WGS84_INVFLATTENING,            //（OGR定义的常数）WGS84椭球体扁率的倒数(298.257223563)\n               &quot;Greenwich&quot;,                        //格林尼治子午线\n               0.0,\n               &quot;degree&quot;,                           //格林尼治子午线单位\n               SRS_UA_DEGREE_CONV                  //（OGR定义的常数）度和弧度的换算比例(0.0174532925199433)\n              );\n\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><code> SetWellKnownGeogCS</code> 使用常用的字符串来定义常用的地理坐标系</p><p>使用 <code>WGS84</code>字符串定义一个<code>WGS84</code>的地理坐标系</p><div class="language-c# ext-c# line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-c#"><code>OGRSpatialReference oSRS;\noSRS.SetWellKnownGeogCS(&quot;WGS84&quot;);\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>使用<code>EPSG</code>代码定义地理坐标系</p><div class="language-c# ext-c# line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-c#"><code>OGRSpatialReference oSRS;\noSRS.SetWellKnownGeogCS(&quot;EPSG:4326&quot;);\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><code>exportToWkt</code> 转为<code>WKT</code>格式</p><div class="language-c# ext-c# line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-c#"><code>Char*pszWKT=null;\nOGRSpatialReference oSRS;\noSRS.SetWellKnownGeogCS(&quot;WGS84&quot;);\noSRS.exportToWkt(pszWKT);\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>输出值为</p><div class="language-xml ext-xml line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-xml"><code>GEOGCS[&quot;WGS 84&quot;,\n\tDATUM[&quot;WGS_1984&quot;,\n\t\tSPHEROID[&quot;WGS 84&quot;,6378137,298.257223563,\n\t\tAUTHORITY[&quot;EPSG&quot;,7030]],\n\tTOWGS84[0,0,0,0,0,0,0],\n\tAUTHORITY[&quot;EPSG&quot;,6326]],\n PRIMEM[&quot;Greenwich&quot;,0,AUTHORITY[&quot;EPSG&quot;,8901]],\nUNIT[&quot;DMSH&quot;,0.0174532925199433,AUTHORITY[&quot;EPSG&quot;,9108]],\nAXIS[&quot;Lat&quot;,NORTH],\nAXIS[&quot;Long&quot;,EAST],\nAUTHORITY[&quot;EPSG&quot;,4326]]\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>如果知道一个<code>WKT</code>定义的坐标系的字符串,我们可以使用类<code>OGRSpatialReference</code>中的函数<code>importFromWkt()</code>构造一个<code>OGRSpatialReference</code>类对象</p>',13),l={},s=(0,i(63243).Z)(l,[["render",function(e,n){return d}]])},63243:(e,n)=>{n.Z=(e,n)=>{const i=e.__vccOpts||e;for(const[e,d]of n)i[e]=d;return i}}}]);